<h6 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">Film</h6>
<p5> I’ve always desired to watch and learn more and do deep dives into director's work, as well as understanding different methods for storytelling and plot development with television. In my first year at Northwestern, I secured a press pass to the Chicago International Film Festival and interviewed Oscar-winner, Emerald Fennell, about her film Saltburn. I have since penned more reviews and had the privilege to interview director Tim Mielants earlier this fall during the festival.</p5>
